title: 007: I've Been On A Diet Since I Was 11 Years Old with Sahara Rose

description:
A short little something spirit channeled through me that I wanted to put into the universe. If you relate to this in any way, please join me and end diet culture. You are so beautiful when you are full.. of joy, of love, of life.

Learn more about me and discover your mind-body type at www.IAmSaharaRose.com

Be part of a community that supports you discovering your dharma in Rose Gold Goddesses, the sacred sisterhood collective with community, content, creativity and so much more — learn more about rosegoldgoddesses.com.
